      "rationale": "Bench tests used bovine blood at 37 °C matching clinical temperature; however hematocrit range (35–45%) only partially overlaps the VAD patient population (25–55%). Inlet velocity profiles measured but not matched to in-vivo conditions. Achieved level 3 against required level 5."
