      "rationale": "Validation used the FDA generic centrifugal pump geometry, which matches the COU geometry. However, operating speed range tested (2000–3000 RPM) does not cover the upper VAD operating range (up to 3500 RPM) specified in the COU. Deviations not formally justified. Achieved level 2 against required level 5."
